observations.recommendation:
We recommended and the Municipal Mayor as well as the Municipal Accountant agreed to direct the Municipal Treasurer to liquidate her cash advances as soon as possible considering that the amounts have already been distributed to the beneficiaries;
We also recommended and the Municipal Accountant agreed to prepare promptly the adjusting journal entries as soon as the Municipal Treasurer submits the Fund Utilization Report (FUR); and
Lastly, we recommended and the Municipal Accountant agreed to strictly require employees with unliquidated cash advance to settle the amount advanced within the prescribed period and ensure that no additional cash advance be granted to any official or employee unless the previous cash advance given to him/her is first settled or proper accounting thereof is made.

